      "type": "paragraph",
      "title": "Result",
      "description": "Bacardi presented its new Caribbean-style rum collection and we were contacted by the London-based agency Big Bad Wolf to produce the corporate video that would accompany the launch. After several creative meetings, we developed a visual proposal aligned with the brand's values: freshness, trajectory and tropical heritage. Our mission was to transform that concept into an audiovisual piece faithful to Bacardi's spirit. The result was a dynamic video that combines brand narrative and dynamism, designed for multiple platforms. The campaign reinforced Bacardi's global presence and highlighted its new line as a celebration of Caribbean identity. This project consolidated our experience in high-level work with global brands, effectively coordinating with international agencies and executing productions with demanding creative standards."
